    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Responsive WPF applications with ReactiveUI]]></title>
    <link href="http://whazzing.com/blog/2013/02/22/responsive-wpf-applications-with-reactiveui/"/>
    <updated>2013-02-22T21:25:00-06:00</updated>
